<bibRefCitation id="A84D4B6FB62AFFBDFA8F8379FA1BD450" author="Assing, V." box="[1308,1436,1033,1055]" pageId="5" pageNumber="221" pagination="1 - 5" refId="ref5096" refString="Assing, V. (2007) A revision of the microphthalmous Lathrobium species of Turkey II. Two new species and an additional record of L. brignolii (Insecta: Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). Entomological Problems, 37, 1 - 5." type="journal article" year="2007">Assing, 2007</bibRefCitation>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CC63369EB62AFFBDFF048356FA1BD416" blockId="5.[151,1437,681,1612]" pageId="5" pageNumber="221">
<keyLead id="772D95ABB62AFFBDFF048356FA1BD416" pageId="5" pageNumber="221">
<emphasis id="FEA8EA8CB62AFFBDFF048356FF24D475" bold="true" box="[151,163,1062,1083]" pageId="5" pageNumber="221">–</emphasis>
Head with shallow microreticulation; pronotum broader in relation to head; posterior incision of male sternite VIII deeper, aedeagus larger, approximately 
<quantity id="0B249B7BB62AFFBDFD808334FDD8D417" box="[531,607,1092,1113]" metricMagnitude="-4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="221" unit="mm" value="0.9">0.9 mm</quantity>
. Distribution: 
